title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine First Look: Jake and The Vulture Bond Over Nip Slips
text: 6:10 PM Updated at 9:43 PM   6:10 PM Updated at 9:43 PM Â» Social News Beware The Vulture! After Brooklyn Nine-Nine 's premiere last week, the 99th Precinct was left with one dead captain (Bill Hader) and a familiar face to take his place: Det. Pembroke, aka The Vulture (guest star Dean Winters ). If you recall, the obnoxious braggart loves attention and always tries to take credit for other people's hard work. So why is Jake ( Andy Samberg ) suddenly wearing puka shell necklaces and bonding with The Vulture over nip slips? Check out this exclusive sneak peek of Sunday's episode to find out: Brooklyn Nine-Nine airs Sundays at 8:30/7:30c on FOX. Other Links From TVGuide.com
